{
  "_about": "Curated interview question bank used as the primary source when no LLM key is configured, and as a fallback when LLM generation fails. Each entry: text, category (hr|technical|behavioral), difficulty (easy|medium|hard), optional company, optional role, expected_keywords (used by the baseline scorer in Phase 7 and the NLP scorer in Phase 9), optional sample_answer.",
